movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: How they have destroyed the spirit of star wars
review: If you want to know the physical component of the force...I have not found the force in this film, except in this ridiculous blood analysis.No soul, no suspense, just some beautiful images, and Nathalie Portman. It's not enough to make a good film. I'll not see the next ones, instead i'll see again the Trilogy.
